comments: Gobert (MIN) is set in Rozier's (CHA) path and marginal contact occurs during the pick.
McDaniels (MIN) lifts his pivot foot as he attempts to split two defenders.
Towns (MIN) reaches across Washington's (CHA) body and delivers lower-body contact as both players go for the loose ball.
Washington (CHA) makes marginal contact with Russell (MIN) as he attempts to go move over the top of the screen attempt.

Replay review of the foul called on Towns (MIN) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Towns jumps from point A to point B and delivers contact to Rozier (CHA) during his driving shot attempt.
Towns (MIN) firms up in Rozier's (CHA) path and marginal contact occurs during the pick.

McDaniels (MIN) makes marginal contact with McDaniels (CHA) as he is securing the loose ball. Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Russell (MIN) cleanly dislodges the ball from Rozier (CHA).
After the ball becomes loose, Russell (MIN) dives over the top of Rozier (CHA) and delivers contact.
Plumlee (CHA) does not establish himself in McDaniels' (MIN) path and does not give him time and space to avoid the contact during the pick.
Russell (MIN) slightly extends his arms into McDaniels (CHA) as he is rolling toward the rim.
As Edwards (MIN) is gathering the ball, incidental contact occurs with Rozier (CHA).
Washington (CHA) briefly grasps Towns' (MIN) arm as he is dribbling the ball in transition, and the contact is marginal.
Gobert (MIN) jumps vertically, collapsing his forearm, and gets to ball height when he cleanly blocks Washington's (CHA) shot attempt. Any ensuing contact is incidental.
Russell (MIN) reaches forward and makes contact with Rozier's (CHA) right arm, causing him to bobble the ball and affecting his ability to cleanly gather it.
Gobert (MIN) legally contests Rozier's (CHA) driving shot attempt.
Russell (MIN) commits a take foul against Washington (CHA).
Washington (CHA) avoids making contact with Gobert (MIN) during the shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the game clock is reset to 00:00.4.
